{"tid":415904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對肥婆有種特別既感覺","createTime":"2017-09-27T11:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T11:52:10.000Z","uid":65051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cbaa367f1192049eb6a8d28d55d568806362c1be","tid":415904,"uid":65051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:04:03.000Z","msg":"有冇Ching同小弟一樣硬係覺得肥婆特別多閪屎同老泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/185716_0d987528b39a884b8e01f0962a498b75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F185716_0d987528b39a884b8e01f0962a498b75.jpg&h=e9fceddf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/185716_cbf8fa1d6064c6e837caab14ab784040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F185716_cbf8fa1d6064c6e837caab14ab784040.jpg&h=b2e3de41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/185717_cbf8fa1d6064c6e837caab14ab784040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F185717_cbf8fa1d6064c6e837caab14ab784040.jpg&h=5af44ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/185717_b45c426199b4caaba2d0f435ff417a38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F185717_b45c426199b4caaba2d0f435ff417a38.jpg&h=9dab31da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42dc6dbfffaba01c988d89fe1f93eef058c70d3f","tid":415904,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:04:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5569c2e096a7788480fcf3b0e5d04dd79f3c87f4","tid":415904,"uid":19502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:04:49.000Z","msg":"大部份肥到成座山咁嘅肥婆，條頸後面都好多老泥，因為佢哋沖涼嘅時候卒唔到。 <br />\n老泥俾頸部脂肪一層層夾住，日復日年復年咁累積。 <br />\n所以大部份肥婆條頸都係黑色，越黑老泥越厚。 <br />\n如果你哋有幸溝到肥婆，就人一世物一世點都要試下。 <br />\n首先用手指濕少少水起勢咁卒，用匙羹刮出嚟，加兩滴美極慢慢品嚐。 <br />\n初哥可能話核突，但你唔食肥婆老泥等於登上白雲山唔食山水豆腐花一樣咁傻的嗎。 <br />\n<br />\n下身方面又係有學問，肥婆食咁多漢堡包同牛肉，男性荷爾蒙分泌過盛。 <br />\n所以塊西至屎o全部都係毛，無論佢幾乾淨，都有陣咸魚溝變壞乳酪嘅味道。 <br />\n據英國研究，82.5%肥婆都唔會剃腳毛，因為烏低身嗰下等於做sit up，有違肥人忠旨。 <br />\n所以肥婆啲腳毛永遠好似鐵線咁粗。 <br />\n奶西嘅時候叫佢瞓低你忠個頭埋去，兩隻手要掃佢隻腳啲鐵線等佢起雞皮，然後叫佢嗰對火腿夾實自己個頭唔好比空氣流出。 <br />\n陣咸魚味喺真空環境會得到昇華，係有層次而漸進的。 <br />\n奶嗰時攝攝聲，有3D立體音響加回音效果。 <br />\n你嗅覺，味覺，觸覺，聽覺得到前所未有嘅享受，呢啲先叫人生啊。 <br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪嗰part唔多講，因為肥婆塊田多肉好撞係常識，你塞咗入去會感受到溫暖同安全感，比一層一層肉緊緊包住。 <br />\n<br />\n成日笑肥婆以為自己好識食嗰啲人，根本就係未夠班，自以為是嘅表現。你比食女界嘅高手揀減肥前欣宜定係整容後楊怡，佢完全唔想答你，一嚟佢唔想笑勁你問無聊野，二嚟佢已經諗緊點班支美極返嚟。"},{"pid":"c3df9099cf2e7f44bbfb57d5d540264f8a2c72c3","tid":415904,"uid":65051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.cat2.me/products/0/0/1/1145741/android/stickers/5941874.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.cat2.me%2Fproducts%2F0%2F0%2F1%2F1145741%2Fandroid%2Fstickers%2F5941874.png&h=c2326152&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥芝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc590ed07f5399a661a456445a33d59ad6d6c52","tid":415904,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:08:15.000Z","msg":"見到啲肥婆就想打鳩佢地 算唔算特別"},{"pid":"ec8648b95d9203019e7274f709110f3f9794376c","tid":415904,"uid":65051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到啲肥婆就想打鳩佢地 算唔算特別</blockquote><br />\n我唔準你咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14013d6511318aa6235e69ea643b97fb642d943","tid":415904,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"特別憎"}]}